{"tid":2421281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好叫劏房波 要叫攬炒波","createTime":"2021-02-24T11:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T14:03:16.000Z","uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56d44ef3fd6ba3c4899f518cbf4510ffb756e221","tid":2421281,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"耀才證券：減稅方可治本 政府不知火燒眼眉 本地, 財經 發佈時間 24.02.2021 19:21 最後更新時間 24.02.2021 19:21 預算案提出上調股票印花稅稅率，由買賣雙方各付0.1%，增至0.13%。耀才證券發聲明，認為長遠減稅才能治本，批評增加印花稅只是小修小補及陰乾式的治標方法，形容政府無視香港已經火燒眼眉。 耀才證券強調，如果稅率吸引，人才及外資企業自然會回流香港，形容五眼聯盟正千方百計誘使香港人才離棄香港，呼籲港府勿令奸計得逞。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380447\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2380447&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8Ex5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=3c76f4c4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380447</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe756519a8adba058f81b2c3fb08fb740e835f8","tid":2421281,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"又加稅攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ce6994cf357592708affb81ed6cb76829a91c5","tid":2421281,"uid":329842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T11:47:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">劫貧濟富陳茂波</span></span>"},{"pid":"18f84d4bb37d6e5f979b7d3af837aaf04a3a6601","tid":2421281,"uid":229270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T12:39:07.000Z","msg":"叫臭閪波"},{"pid":"41bc9842551803eb3ccc8e3728ca90f94624ff8f","tid":2421281,"uid":232237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86ce6994cf357592708affb81ed6cb76829a91c5","tid":2421281,"uid":329842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"